casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Link.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Link (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 1204.]

(No. 91-1925 Submitted October 9, 1991 Decided October 10, 1991.)

On Motion to Withdraw Affidavit of Resignation.

The motion of Wayne Eugene Link, Registration No. 0021473, to withdraw affidavit of resignation is granted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
